<article class="row-fluid">
  <div class="span12 columns">

    <%= link_to 'New Colophon', new_colophon_path %>

    <header class="row-fluid page-header">
      <h1 class="first"><span class="t">T</span><small><span class="firstLine">he colophon is a brief description of the 'making of' a book.</span><span class="small"><sup class="footnote fn1"><a href="/colophon#fn1">[1]</a></sup> The making of <em>this</em> book has been far from brief; it involved not only the research and writing of the content for this project, but also the design and development of this website, which is where I will begin.</span></small>
      </h1>
    </header>

    <section class="row-fluid">
      <div class="span7 columns pull-left">
        <p>Setting up my work environment required the installation of a number of primary development tools, which were installed in the same order listed here.</p>

        <section class="row-fluid span12">
          <div class="span4">
            <% @colophons.each do |colophon| %>
            <a href="#" class="thumbnail">
              <img src="http://placehold.it/100x100" alt="">
            </a>
              <p><%= raw colophon.name %> <%= raw colophon.description %> <%= link_to 'Show', colophon %>
              </p>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</article>